  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Left ventricular dyssynchrony will be assessed by echocardiography using different
      programming of an implantable cardioverter defibrillator.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Left ventricular dyssynchrony will be assessed by echocardiography using different
      programming of an implantable cardioverter defibrillator using a quadripolar left ventricular
      lead.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
